high_descs: move to the sink to the left of the stove
pick up a cup from the cabinet under the sink
move to the microwave to the left
heat up the cup in the microwave
move to the sink to the right
put the cup in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward and stand at the sink.
Open the cabinet under the sink and take out a glass.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Heat the glass in the microwave.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed glass in the sink.

high_descs: Move across the room to the sink just to the left of the stove.
Open the cabinet under the sink and take out the vase.
Turn left and move to the microwave.
Put the vase in the microwave to the left of the egg. Warm it for a few seconds and then remove it from the microwave.
Turn right and head back to the sink.
Set the vase down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the warmed up vase in the sink.
